✅ 2. Git & GitHub Setup Commands
Initialize Git
bash
Copy code
git init
Basic Git Commands
bash
Copy code
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit"
Link GitHub Repo
bash
Copy code
git remote add origin https://github.com/your-username/your-repo.git
git push -u origin main
✅ 3. HTML5 Fundamentals Code Examples
✔ Basic HTML Structure using semantic tags
html
Copy code
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>HTML5 Structure</title>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Welcome to My Website</h1>
</header>

<nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a> |
    <a href="#">About</a> |
    <a href="#">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section>
    <h2>Section Title</h2>
    <p>This is a section paragraph.</p>
</section>

<article>
    <h2>Article Title</h2>
    <p>This is an article paragraph.</p>
</article>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 My Website</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
✔ HTML5 Form Example
html
Copy code
<form>
    <label>Name:</label>
    <input type="text" name="name"><br><br>

    <label>Select Gender:</label>
    <label><input type="radio" name="gender" value="male"> Male</label>
    <label><input type="radio" name="gender" value="female"> Female</label><br><br>

    <label>Choose Skills:</label>
    <input type="checkbox" name="skills" value="html"> HTML
    <input type="checkbox" name="skills" value="css"> CSS
    <input type="checkbox" name="skills" value="js"> JavaScript<br><br>

    <label>Select Country:</label>
    <select>
        <option>India</option>
        <option>USA</option>
    </select><br><br>

    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
</form>
✔ Multimedia Embeds (audio, video, iframe)
html
Copy code
<video width="400" controls>
    <source src="video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>

<audio controls>
    <source src="audio.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
</audio>

<iframe width="400" height="250" src="https://youtube.com/embed/example"></iframe>
✔ Table Example with <thead>, <tbody>, <tfoot>
html
Copy code
<table border="1">
    <thead>
        <tr><th>Name</th><th>Age</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr><td>John</td><td>25</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Ana</td><td>22</td></tr>
    </tbody>
    <tfoot>
        <tr><td colspan="2">End of Data</td></tr>
    </tfoot>
</table>
✅ 4. CSS3 Styling Examples
✔ Inline, Internal, External CSS
html
Copy code
<p style="color: blue;">This is inline CSS text.</p>

<style>
    p { color: green; }
</style>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
✔ Flexbox Layout
css
Copy code
.container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
}
✔ Grid Layout
css
Copy code
.grid-box {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
}
✔ Shadows, Borders, Gradients
css
Copy code
.box {
    border: 2px solid #333;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #4facfe, #00f2fe);
}
✔ Basic Animation
css
Copy code
@keyframes moveBox {
    from { transform: translateX(0); }
    to { transform: translateX(100px); }
}

.animate {
    animation: moveBox 2s infinite alternate;
}
✔ Media Query (Responsive Design)
css
Copy code
@media (max-width: 600px) {
    body {
        background-color: lightyellow;
    }
}
